               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18480821-name-151" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-151" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-151" type="surname" value="HARBOUR"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-151" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM HARBOUR</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at Harlingdon. I had a gun at Mr. Cole<lb></lb>man's, where I worked, and a powder-flask and shot-bag with it, which belonged to Mr. Coleman—I put them in a cart in the shed, on Tuesday night, 8th Aug.—I missed them on Wednesday, at one o'clock—these are them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18480821-name-152" type="witnessName">
